trans-unit.source: Contains an event opcode that is defined in an event provider.
trans-unit.target: 包含事件 opcode 事件提供者中所定義。

trans-unit.source: An opcode defines a numeric value that identifies the activity or a point within an activity that the application was performing when it raised the event.
trans-unit.target: Opcode 定義數值的值，識別活動或活動中的應用程式執行時引發事件的點。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.Reader.ProviderMetadata> object defies a list of EventOpcode objects, one for each opcode defined in the provider.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.Reader.ProviderMetadata>物件沒有 EventOpcode 物件清單，其中每個提供者中定義的 opcode。</xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.Reader.ProviderMetadata>

trans-unit.source: The standard event opcodes are defined in the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.Reader.StandardEventOpcode> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 中所定義的標準事件 opcode<xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.Reader.StandardEventOpcode>列舉型別。</xref:System.Diagnostics.Eventing.Reader.StandardEventOpcode>

trans-unit.source: Gets the localized name for an event opcode.
trans-unit.target: 取得事件 opcode 的當地語系化的名稱。

trans-unit.source: Returns a string that contains the localized name for an event opcode.
trans-unit.target: 傳回包含事件 opcode 的當地語系化的名稱的字串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the non-localized name for an event opcode.
trans-unit.target: 取得事件 opcode 的非當地語系化名稱。

trans-unit.source: Returns a string that contains the non-localized name for an event opcode.
trans-unit.target: 傳回包含事件 opcode 的非當地語系化名稱的字串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the numeric value associated with the event opcode.
trans-unit.target: 取得與事件作業碼相關聯的數值。
